    - RatesAndCommission
      - RatePlanList with details; commissionModel selector; auto-calc summary
    - PaymentScheduleEditor
      - Milestone items with date pickers, amount fields, currency, methods
      - Validation for conflicts with booking dates and deadlines
    - ItineraryEditor
      - DayEditor: add day, add activities/transfers, times, durations
      - Drag-and-drop order; conflicts checks (overlaps)
    - AttachmentsAndSuppliers
      - Upload attachments; capture supplier references; map to booking line items
    - ReviewAndActions
      - Summary view; validation panel; actions: Save Draft, Save as Quote, Confirm Booking
    - ProposalHandoverGenerator
      - Generate DOCX/PDF proposals using booking data; templates populated from state
    - BookingDetailTimeline
      - Timeline of lifecycle stages; filters by date range
